      <p>When you call (323) 990-7550, here's what happens: we'll ask a few quick questions about your LG dryer symptoms and schedule a same-day appointment. Our tech arrives with common parts already on the truck and diagnoses the heating problem for $65. If you approve the repair, we waive that diagnostic fee and fix it on the spot — 85% of our calls get resolved the same visit. We only use OEM LG parts and back everything with our warranty. Same-day service runs Monday through Saturday, 8am to 8pm.</p>
